metadata.name: Zephyrion
metadata.description:
In a realm beyond our own,  
Where the unknown lies unknown,  
Lies a parallel dimension,  
Where overlords hold ascension.

Mysterious and enigmatic,  
Their power, truly cinematic,  
Shaping reality at will,  
Their essence, beyond human still.

A cosmic awe and wonder,  
A call to expand and ponder,  
For the mysteries that it holds,  
Are stories yet to be told.

Inviting us to reach beyond,  
To seek and embrace the bond,  
Of the universe's profound,  
And the enigmas yet to be found.

Thus, the overlords in their reign,  
Bring us lessons to ascertain,  
And inspire us to seek and soar,  
To find what the universe has in store.
